title: Rage at Dawn (1955 American Technicolor Western film) Randolph Scott, Forrest Tucker, Mala Powers

sources.title: Rage at Dawn (1955 American Technicolor Western film) Randolph Scott, Forrest Tucker, Mala Powers
sources.description:
Showdown at Sunup! Randolph Scott goes undercover to smoke out the Reno Brothers.
In the Wild West, special agent James Barlow, is on a mission to capture the corrupt Reno brothers. After attracting the Renos' attention Barlow infiltrates the gang and forms a perilous romance with their sister, Laura. As tensions escalate, Barlow strategizes a daring plan to trap the Renos during a high-stakes train robbery.

Original title: Rage at Dawn (1955) AKA: Seven Bad Men

This film is available in English, German, Italian & Spanish audio, and subtitled in many more language options.

Director: Tim Whelan
Writers: Horace McCoy, Frank Gruber 
Stars: Randolph Scott, Forrest Tucker, Mala Powers, J. Carrol Naish 
Genre: Classics, Action & Adventure, Crime, Drama, Western
